raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "scheil" %}
{% set version = "0.1.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "de43e05fb9fdfb084fa3c7709000cc81c88292eaee24a0ac020c52c032c0c809" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3
    - numpy
    - scipy
    - pycalphad >=0.8.1

test:
  imports:
    - scheil
    - scheil.simulate
    - scheil.solidification_result
    - scheil.utils

about:
  home: https://scheil.readthedocs.io
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A Scheil-Gulliver simulation tool using pycalphad'
  doc_url: A Scheil-Gulliver simulation tool using pycalphad
  dev_url: https://github.com/pycalphad/scheil

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bocklund
    - richardotis
